description:
A verry good collection for french speakers. As we know, great comics such as Tintin, Asterix and Lucky-Luke are originally phrancophone. Here is a great opportunity to have the whole collection of these three classics!

Tintin and Lucky-Luke books are in pdf format. For the Asterix comics you will need a comics client to open the files. They are.cbr files (official comic files extention).

Tintin and Asterix comics are in great shape and very good quality. The Lucky-Luke ones vary in quality, once they are more difficult to find.
However, they are all in different folders. So you may keep what's interesting for you. But I organized them myself and I must say that it's pretty decent.
